Sources: Code "E" 111 Sqn. Undercarriage collapsed/wheels up landing at Wattisham on 10/12/1973 resulted in damage beyond economic repair. It was struck off charge on 07/01/1974 for spares use. Stripped for spares in June 1974 and placed on the dump at Wattisham.
